Job Details
Required Arabic Sr. Administration Officer/ Assistant Administration Manager for a leading contracting company in Abu Dhabi.
Relevant candidate should have:
Immense experience(minimum 5 years in Abu Dhabi) in handling all governmental issues of an Organization ,controlling & handling PROs. Should be able to do prioritize tasks, distribute, follow up and complete on time. Only Arabic nationalities with UAE DL are preferred for this position.
Salary is commensurate to your level of experience and qualification.
